'''Barq''' was an expensive [[Cereal/Legends|cereal]] used in luxury restaurants all over [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. The pearl-like grains were native to the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] world of [[Qiilura/Legends|Qiilura]] which had a musky, almost fungal smell.

==History==
During the time of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], the barq exports from Qiilura were controlled by the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]]. Moreover, during [[Omega Squad]]'s [[mission to Qiilura]], the Trade Federation significantly raised the barq price due to the collateral damage dealt to a couple of barq fields and farms by the [[Clone commando/Legends|clone commandos]] and some of [[Ghez Hokan]]'s more unruly troops.

